snippet: Officers who stopped a van in Imperial County, in the state's southeast corner, discovered 29 illegal immigrants crowded inside, the California Highway Patrol said today....
lead_paragraph: Officers who stopped a van in Imperial County, in the state's southeast corner, discovered 29 illegal immigrants crowded inside, the California Highway Patrol said today.
abstract: Highway patrol officers find 29 illegal Mexican aliens crowded in van after stopping vehicle in Interstate highway near Seeley, Calif; all are returned to Mexico (S)

headline.main: Van Stopped by Police Is Full of Illegal Aliens
